channel.title: I'm finally coming back to RS :)
channel.description: After over a year, my friend and I have both decided to come back to RuneScape and make new pures to be better than ever before. We currently both own main accounts, mine being lvl 112 and his being 91 but neither have memberships. We are making our pure mages members and we need some cash to start out with. I was wondering if anyone would be willing to donate 200k gp or 15k-25k fire runes and 15k-25k mind runes so we can get to training ASAP. =)
